4 sloh me seo sunne on ðone swiðran eaxl, 5 seo þe, beorhte scín, ealne westan 6 awende to hwítre hiwe of haswon;
7 and ic mid ðære sceade geworhte ðæt fyr 8 ðuhte ða swiðor byrnende; and þeah ðurh ðæt tacen ana 9 ic geseah fela sceada, þa we forð gewendon, georne behealdan.

